Class MappingCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.datamelt.rules.core.util.MappingCollection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class MappingCollection
extends Object
implements Serializable
    collection containing maps of key/value pairs. these maps can be used to replace - using an action - the original value with a value defined in a mapping file. The mapping file is identified by it's filename.
